<%= content_for :title, "Happening Now - Project Pitch" %>

<div class="wrapper">
    <p class="group-members">April Park, Desean Abraham, Mike Alicea, Bob Shannon</p> 
    
    <section>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h2 class="panel-title"><i class="fa fa-puzzle-piece"></i> The Problem</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>65% of people in the age range of 18-25 do not vote. This generation also happens to be the largest generation that has spawned in this United States ever.  With the amount of people that are eligible to vote that do not we would have a serious impact on the popular vote.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h2 class="panel-title"><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> The Solution</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>UBVoting is a web app that displays information on current presidential candidates. Information is drawn in from different sources like news articles, Reddit, Twitter, YouTube, and Facebook. The primary function of UBVoting is to encourage college students to stay informed and vote and be a one stop shop to gather various info on candidates quickly.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h2 class="panel-title"><i class="fa fa-list-ol"></i> Project Phases</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <span class="badge">Deadline: October 16th, 2015</span>
                        <h3 class="list-group-item-heading">Phase 1: Static Prototype</h3>
                        <ul class="list-group-item-text">
                                <li>Proof of concept</li>
                                <li>Get wireframes coded, placeholders to look at</li>
                                <li>Clearly see what nuances and improvements can be made</li>
                                <li>Gain familiarity with the technologies used (HTML5/CSS3/Compass/JS) and team personalities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>

                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <span class="badge">Deadline: November 11th, 2015</span>
                        <h3 class="list-group-item-heading">Phase 2: Dynamic Prototype</h3>
                        <ul class="list-group-item-text">
                            <li>Scrap proof of concept</li>
                            <li>Add functionality, unify look and feel of all pages</li>
                            <li>Improve look and feel of all pages</li>
                            <li>Incorporation of dynamic information, pull data from APIâ€™s</li>
                            <li>Choose backend and frontend frameworks</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>

                     <li class="list-group-item">
                        <span class="badge">Deadline: December 11th, 2015</span>
                        <h3 class="list-group-item-heading">Phase 3: Welcome the Beta</h3>
                        <ul class="list-group-item-text">
                            <li>Implement backend API</li>
                            <li>Incorporate wishlist features</li>
                            <li>Further tweaking of look and feel</li>
                            <li>Continue the hunt for bugs</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h2 class="panel-title"><i class="fa fa-picture-o"></i> Phase 1 Wireframe Mockups</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="panel-body">
                <div id="carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                    <!-- Indicators -->
                    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                        <li data-target="#carousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                    </ol>

                    <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
                    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                        <div class="item active">
                            <img src="/images/wireframes/candidates.png" alt="">
                        </div>

                        <div class="item">
                            <img src="/images/wireframes/events.png" alt="">
                        </div>

                        <div class="item">
                            <img src="/images/wireframes/candidates-list.png" alt="">
                        </div>

                        <div class="item">
                            <img src="/images/wireframes/states-alt.png" alt="">
                        </div>

                        <div class="item">
                            <img src="/images/wireframes/home.png" alt="">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Controls -->
                    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
